{"tid":843005,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【封鎖新疆？】王毅稱「再教育營」是必要措施：讓2,000萬新疆人安心睡覺","createTime":"2018-09-30T18:31:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T04:58:19.000Z","uid":47714,"like":6,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"5f942a9b570ed0974d110b2ed461ca7478ebebdd","tid":843005,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T18:31:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180930/58741148\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180930%2F58741148&d=2QK0a6bb97fHFihUU1LPWsKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=a0ab4d60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180930%2F58741148&h=fe265911\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180930/58741148</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180930/bkn-20180930181729227-0930_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20180930%2Fbkn-20180930181729227-0930_00952_001.html&d=2QK0a6bb97fHFihUU1LPWsKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=ecee19e7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180930/bkn-20180930181729227-0930_00952_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180930/large/1538288605_4d6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180930%2Flarge%2F1538288605_4d6a.jpg&h=866e9eb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新疆無預警停售下月22日以後的火車車票，直至另行通告為止，各界都質疑新疆的局勢不穩。聯合國消除種族歧視委員會上月發表的報告指出，中共在新疆廣設「再教育營」，關押逾百萬維吾爾族人，引起各國關注。可是中國外交部長王毅在聯合國大會上發言時，指再教育營是要讓「新疆2,000萬民眾感覺到安全，到了晚上可以安心睡覺」的必要措施。<br />\n<br />\n王毅在聯合國，沒有否認再教育營的存在，聲稱這是中共為要反恐的「必要措施」，「負責任的必要措施」，他強調「新疆2,000萬民眾感覺到了安全，因為到了晚上可以安心睡覺了。不會再受到暴力恐怖主義的襲擊了。這是中國政府為老百姓做的好事情」。<br />\n<br />\n內地的統計顯示，新疆2,181萬人口當中，維吾爾族人口佔45%，中共大量轉移人口，令到漢族人口增至40%，維漢衝突一直存在，2009年7月5日鳥魯木齊爆發造成197人死亡、1,721人受傷的暴力事件後，當局在這次事件後，派出大量軍警到當地「維穩」，同時不斷打擊新疆各地的「三股勢力」（暴力恐怖勢力、民族分裂勢力、宗教極端勢力），大量被指涉及暴力事件的維族人被判刑，不少人權組織都指摘中共在新疆大規模侵犯人權，甚至稱新疆為「露天大監獄」。<br />\n<br />\n在新疆的「再教育營」營裏，官員禁止維族人進行宗教活動、不斷讚頌中共等，不少從外國回到新疆，即被關押在再教育營。<br />\n<br />\n對於新疆的再教育營，聯合國消除種族歧視委員會呼籲中共終止在沒有合法指控、審判和定罪的情況下進行拘留，立即釋放目前被拘留的人，提供被拘留者的人數，並拘留他們的理由，與及對所有涉及種族、民族和民族宗教有關的指控進行公正調查。"},{"pid":"d243e3ab3ce9ac40dde821168208f7b49f8f776b","tid":843005,"uid":47714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T18:32:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://unpo.org/article/21117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Funpo.org%2Farticle%2F21117&d=2QK0a6bb97fHFihUU1LPWsKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=616f7824\" target=\"_blank\">http://unpo.org/article/21117</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://unpo.org/imgi/p/6913.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Funpo.org%2Fimgi%2Fp%2F6913.jpg&h=53963fdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNew York: Canada has called out China for its human right abuses, notably of the Muslim Uighurs, officials said Tuesday [25 September 2018].<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Every single time I sit down with any world leader, but particularly ones where there are human rights concerns, I bring up human rights,&rdquo; Prime Minister Justin Trudeau said on the sidelines of the United Nations General Assembly.<br />\n<br />\nUp to one million Uighurs and other Muslim minorities have been detained in internment camps in China&rsquo;s far western Xinjiang region, according to estimates cited by the UN Committee on the Elimination of Racial Discrimination.<br />\n<br />\nCanada&rsquo;s Foreign Minister Chrystia Freeland said she met on Monday [24 September 2018] with her Chinese counterpart, Wang Yi, &ldquo;and I did raise the issue of the Uighurs.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;We who live in freedom do have an obligation to stand up for people who don&rsquo;t,&rdquo; she said.<br />\n<br />\nBeijing has disputed the findings of the UN report, saying the actions were necessary to combat extremism and terrorism on the country&rsquo;s western frontier, on the border with Pakistan."},{"pid":"826b8809720b925b9366bc8c763a977d4a60e164","tid":843005,"uid":21545,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T18:33:04.000Z","msg":"佢痴Q咗線.jpg <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e19f6e07e524d685d75e726417475c950b4547ce","tid":843005,"uid":36421,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T18:35:15.000Z","msg":"好快到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6fb7a4cce2497864b8e9367564b964cf718c91e","tid":843005,"uid":51620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T18:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e7ec89719929fe71b6ac3ac58e0f9bdb4a3d5e","tid":843005,"uid":45788,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T18:59:04.000Z","msg":"支持中共一帶一路去中東搞再教育營<br />\n<br />\n中東人民安心睡覺，唔會有恐怖襲擊了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303bc9fb4959fb9ef416a4e2950f5b698ced3064","tid":843005,"uid":74778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"03e7ec89719929fe71b6ac3ac58e0f9bdb4a3d5e","tid":843005,"uid":45788,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T18:59:04.000Z","msg":"支持中共一帶一路去中東搞再教育營<br />\n<br />\n中東人民安心睡覺，唔會有恐怖襲擊了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T19:00:56.000Z","msg":"中東都教得掂，聯合國係咪放佢"},{"pid":"c2925be92d1e6032d4be6a47ffeed6064a97643f","tid":843005,"uid":91982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T19:32:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cbb20c6f6e371c47b8d0e71758f8ddf050c9e027","tid":843005,"uid":49955,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2